<h1>Shield Support - Staffing Detailed Overview</h1>

<h2>2. Staffing Services</h2>
<p>Specialized staffing tiers to build your ideal technical team.</p>

<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>NOC Staffing (Network Operations Center)</strong>
        <br><em>Description:</em> Expert teams dedicated to the 24/7 monitoring and management of your network infrastructure.
        <br><em>Roles & Responsibilities:</em>
        <ul>
            <li>Continuous monitoring of network health and performance.</li>
            <li>Incident response and fault management.</li>
            <li>Reporting and documentation of network events.</li>
            <li>Coordination with third-party vendors and ISPs.</li>
        </ul>
        <em>Ideal For:</em> MSPs and enterprises needing round-the-clock eyes on their critical infrastructure.
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Cyber Security Staffing</strong>
        <br><em>Description:</em> Highly trained security professionals focused on protecting your digital environment.
        <br><em>Roles & Responsibilities:</em>
        <ul>
            <li>Security Operations Center (SOC) analysts.</li>
            <li>Threat hunters and incident responders.</li>
            <li>Compliance analysts (HIPAA, GDPR, SOC2).</li>
            <li>Security engineers for tool implementation.</li>
        </ul>
        <em>Ideal For:</em> Organizations with strict compliance needs or those facing high threat levels.
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Cloud Computing Staffing</strong>
        <br><em>Description:</em> Specialists in designing, migrating, and managing cloud environments.
        <br><em>Roles & Responsibilities:</em>
        <ul>
            <li>Cloud Architects (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud).</li>
            <li>DevOps engineers for automation and CI/CD pipelines.</li>
            <li>Cloud migration specialists.</li>
            <li>Infrastructure-as-Code (IaC) developers.
        </ul>
        <em>Ideal For:</em> Businesses moving to the cloud or optimizing their existing cloud footprint.
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Help Desk Staffing</strong>
        <br><em>Description:</em> Front-line support agents who serve as the face of your IT department.
        <br><em>Roles & Responsibilities:</em>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Level 1:</strong> Ticket triage, password resets, basic troubleshooting.</li>
            <li><strong>Level 2:</strong> Desktop support, software installation, complex issue resolution.</li>
            <li><strong>Level 3:</strong> Advanced problem solving, server-side troubleshooting, root cause analysis.
        </ul>
        <em>Ideal For:</em> Scaling support teams to handle increased ticket volume and improving customer satisfaction scores.
    </li>
</ul>

